sections.text: Physician, defined.Physician shall mean a person with an unlimited license to practice medicine in this state pursuant to the Medicine and Surgery Practice Act or a person with a license to practice osteopathic medicine or osteopathic medicine and surgery in this state pursuant to sections 38-2029 to 38-2033.SourceLaws 1976, LB 434, ยง 4;Laws 1988, LB 1100, ยง 3;Laws 2007, LB463, ยง 1136.Cross ReferencesMedicine and Surgery Practice Act, see section 38-2001.
